Review this Horses Hub page at 325px width (small phone). These are screenshots showing the full page scroll (WITHOUT chat engaged yet). Check for:
1. Layout overflow - anything extending past viewport?
2. Touch targets - buttons/links at least 44px?
3. Text readability - font sizes adequate?
4. Navigation usability - section nav buttons
5. Input area usability
6. Any visual bugs

Be specific about any issues. Include CSS selectors if possible.
